Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reportInstPad(25.10)                                      reportInstPad(25.10)

Name
       reportInstPad - Reports the padding for a specific instance, or all in-
       stance padding in the design

Syntax
        reportInstPad {<instName> | -all}

       Reports the padding for a specific instance, or all instance padding in
       the design. This command can be used if there is instance padding spec-
       ified.

Parameters
       -all   Reports all instance padding in the design.

       <instName>
              Reports the padding for the specified instance.

Example
       The  following  command  reports  the  padding for a specified instance
       named U19567:

       reportInstPad U19567

       It outputs following:

       Padding for Instant [U19567] is 2.

